h6.Problem
Misbehavior while playing a sound object with 'preload' set as true. The sound will present a 2 secs delay.

Please use attached mp3 sound files.

h6.Tested on
iOS simulator 4.3 - Both SDKs works fine but device
iPod device > TiSDK 1.7.2 - OK
iPod device > TiSDK 1.8 CI Build - Crashes the app

h6.Repro sequence
Run the attached app.js
